{
  "title": "Lacquered Canadian Chicken Wings Casserole",
  "description": "A dense, resinous casserole of glazed chicken wings cooked in a clay pot, infused with maple syrup, soy sauce, and herbs for a uniquely Canadian flavor.",
  "cuisine": "Canadian",
