  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 180°C and lightly coat a clay pot with olive oil.",
    "In a bowl combine butter, maple syrup, soy sauce, minced garlic, diced onion, thyme, lemon zest, salt, and pepper to make a glaze.",
    "Arrange the chicken wings in the clay pot and pour the glaze over them, ensuring each wing is coated.",
    "Cover the pot with a lid and bake for 20 minutes, then uncover and bake for an additional 25 minutes until wings are golden and cooked through.",
    "Once done, remove from oven and let the casserole rest for 5 minutes before serving."
  ],
